{"tid":479581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢到盡頭] 廣源邨謀殺案提堂被告零反應　官問有無呼吸","createTime":"2017-11-25T09:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T11:32:08.000Z","uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"928b0f10669088d7a525b6ef8845a66438e54af9","tid":479581,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T09:18:12.000Z","msg":"沙田廣源邨公園周三(22日)發生穿心刀謀殺案，77歲老翁黎萬生被控一項謀殺罪，今日(25日)在沙田法院提堂。被告暫時毋須答辯，續還押監房看管至明年1月5日，以等候涉案生果刀的法證檢驗報告。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">被告坐着輪椅由警員推出庭應訊，但他全程低着頭閉着眼，對裁判官的提問完全無反應，其靜止程度連裁判官亦不禁問警員：「佢有無呼吸㗎？」</span></span>更一度押後案件給當值律師再跟被告會面。辯方律師就堅持跟被告會面時，對方雖表現半睡半醒，但都算有反應，甚至會簡單回應提問。裁判官遂表示：「咁我當佢特登(不作反應)」，並繼續按一般程序處理案件。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，77歲被告黎萬生，報稱退休人士，涉嫌於11月22日沙田廣源邨廣源社區中心外謀殺73歲男子潘國民。"},{"pid":"f6a185636a31e1a51cc72d3281ebe6f061a373d5","tid":479581,"uid":51828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T09:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee61b8e96bd6a53a1d2bd6649fb5811d14aaa74","tid":479581,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0424005767e3019ef93f9ffcba06edc20be4683f","tid":479581,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bf178dbf11bfd3cb945a8557ac7bdf2fbd8c35","tid":479581,"uid":47645,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:16:19.000Z","msg":"正 雙殺廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb43bfd449f5c7223febd189c19ebda08eed9780","tid":479581,"uid":71342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"唔理咁多，即刻訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6421edbad6517b22b5ea8db0037a796283c98c22","tid":479581,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":